[resource]
script = ExtResource("3_5ktal")
id = "delete_node"
title = "Delete node from scene"
description = "**Purpose**
Delete a node instance from an existing Godot scene.

**Usage notes**
- The `scene_path` parameter specifies which scene to modify.
- The `node_path` parameter specifies the scene-tree path of the node to delete.

**Example**
scene_path: res://scenes/main_scene.tscn
node_path: Main/CharacterLayer/Player"
category = ExtResource("1_yorl0")
parameters = Array[ExtResource("2_83bdl")]([SubResource("Resource_q3wrl"), SubResource("Resource_7l1sm"), ExtResource("8_8dmcy")])
options = Array[ExtResource("1_258yj")]([ExtResource("3_7juj8"), ExtResource("4_bmsf7"), ExtResource("5_47hag"), ExtResource("6_x040a")])
